<h4 class="subsubsection"> 5.12.2.4 Action Section </h4>

<p>This section describes the action section.
</p>
<a name="1"></a>
<h4 class="subsubheading"> Sequences and Triggers </h4>

<p>With the sequences and triggers section you can define actions and
interactions on objects in your map file. These sections are used to drive
the engine sequence manager (see section <a href="Sequence-Manager.html#0">Sequence Manager</a>).
</p>


